{
  "name": "Typhoon Release Tempest Step",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Fushin.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You coalesce a powerful gust of wind at your feet, allowing for a burst of quick movement. Choose an unoccupied space within 30 feet in any direction, including up. Each creature you pass within 5 feet of during this movement must make a Dexterity saving throw, being knocked prone on a failed save. This movement does not provoke an attack of opportunity.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the distance you move by 10 feet.</p>",
